{"tid":2186861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報：不會正式支持Trump或Biden當選","createTime":"2020-09-03T09:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T13:24:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"063c12c95ad8800394308f476f2ffb8bdb7bb3f7","tid":2186861,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報文章支持Trump連任，比法新社記者狙擊。<br />\n黎智英助手Mark Simon回應指文章只代表作者個人立場，但又指出Trump政府比Obama政府更支持香港，佢自己上年夏天和年尾都曾經去過美國白宮，可以做証。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2186722/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2186722/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而家，Mark Simon明確指出蘋果日報不會正式公開支持美國總統大選既任何候選人。（We don't do endorsements.  ）<br />\n但Mark Simon也指很多香港人都滿意Trump政府，亦重覆指出Biden團隊拒見香港抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f05ptRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff05ptRE.png&h=eb96060a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ue4hORF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUe4hORF.png&h=b988f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1301436022216065024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1301436022216065024&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=0f2dbfc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1301436022216065024&h=176e447a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1301436022216065024</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1301383897029246982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1301383897029246982&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=7d1dc4cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F13013838970292